By Ayodeji Alabi Akure – Gov. Oluwarotimi Akeredolu of Ondo State on Wednesday approved the appointment of Mrs Margaret Atere as his Senior Special Assistant on Women Affairs. Mr Olusegun Ajiboye, Chief Press Secretary to the governor, in a statement in Akure, said the appointment was with immediate effect. “Akeredolu congratulate the appointee as she join the governor to further push forward efforts aimed at developing the state,”he said.(NAN)